Interface StateChangeListener<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of object whose state is listened

    public interface StateChangeListener<T>
    A generic interface for listening when an object's state changes. The reasons for triggering a state change event vary between classes.
    Author:
    Marko Tuominen
